```gitignore
# Ignore build directories
cmake-build-*/

# Ignore CMake generated files
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
CMakeScripts/
Testing/
Makefile
cmake_install.cmake
CTestTestfile.cmake
*.cmake

# Ignore IDE-specific files
.idea/
*.iml

# Ignore compiled object files and binaries
*.o
*.obj
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll
*.exe
*.out
*.a
*.lib

# Ignore logs and temporary files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp
*.swo
*.DS_Store

# Ignore user-specific files
*.user
*.user.*.json
```

Save this file as `.gitignore` in the root of your repository.